name: #25 The Blood of those Royals
description: A kingdom is not a kingdom and royalty cannot reign supreme if there is no one to pledge loyalty to them. And so, once they settled amongst the stars, in their infinite wisdom, they found a way to pull other beings from the same darkness they had once crawled out of.\n\n[Season 1, Chapter 3 - The Blood of those Royals](https://eyeverse.world/chapter-3)
